data.description: WELCOME HOME TO COVINGTON GA! NO HOA! SOLD AS IS! THIS HOME IS LOCATED ON A CULDE SAC ON A LARGE LOT WITH LOTS OF PRIVACY. IT HAS LOTS OF ROOM AND POTENTIAL FOR A GROWING FAMILY. IT INCLUDES 3 BEDROOMS AND  2 BATHS ON THE MAIN FLOOR AND AN ADDITIONAL BEDROOM, LOFT, OFFICE AND BATHROOM ON THE SECOND FLOOR. THIS 2 STORY HOME HAS SOMETHING FOR EVERYONE! IT INCLUDES A GREAT ROOM ON THE FIRST WITH EAT IN KITCHEN AND FORMAL DINING AREA. THERE IS A GARDEN TUB AND SEPERATE SHOWER IN THE MASTER WITH DOUBLE VANITY. THE LARGE DECK IS GREAT FOR A PRIVATE EVENT ALSO! SELLER WILL REPLACE THE CARPET.
